    "description": "Evergreen India Ventures Solutions, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Distribution Manager for our Bengaluru operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Evergreen India Ventures Solutions:\nEvergreen India Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Ensure proper handling, packaging, and labeling of goods\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Coordinate with customer service teams to resolve delivery issues\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in Cold Chain Logistics\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Flexible working hours\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bengaluru, Karnataka, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Evergreen India Ventures Solutions!",
